This package mirrors, byte-for-byte, the receipt-signing preimage and JCS canonicalization
rules defined by the parent `noa-receipt` package (src/signing.ts, src/canonicalize.ts,
src/jcs.ts, src/types.ts) so that every shell (PWA, native app, server) that imports THIS
module produces signatures and receipts identical to what `noa-receipt` itself produces. See
this package's README.md for the parity gates that enforce that guarantee mechanically.
